name: Socially Promiscuous Garden
description:
Take a walk in our socially promiscuous NFT garden. This garden is designed to help one explore the shifting, evolving nature of crypto and NFT art.Take the perspective of the Artist, Developer, Collector, of Founder. 

What will grow from this NFT garden? What life forms will take root? What will decay and die? What will happen that we never thought possible? 

Dive in and explore our socially promiscuous garden.
